### âœ… Philosophy

- No ORM â€œmagicâ€ â€” only explicit SQLAlchemy 2.0 APIs  
- One repository â†’ one model  
- Predictable transaction scope  
- Works with Pydantic DTOs or dataclasses  
- 100 % type-safe
